      "text": [
        "3681 - وَ قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِيَّاكُمْ وَ اَلدَّيْنَ فَإِنَّهُ هَمٌّ بِاللَّيْلِ وَ ذُلٌّ بِالنَّهَارِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3681 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"Beware of debt, for it is worry at night and humiliation during the day.\""
        ]
      }
    }
